MTN has published its September deals brochure, which includes a Mega Deal that offers users 210GB of data for R599 per month. The deal includes the following: The mobile operator is also offering a 50GB Anytime Data + 50GB Night Express version of this deal with 20GB of video streaming data for R399 per month. It will also continue to offer the 20GB, 40GB, and 80GB SIM-only Mega Deals, which have been available since last month. All of MTN’s Mega Deals require users to sign up to a 24-month contract. The full list of MTN’s Mega Deals is detailed below, along with the promotional data included for each deal. It should be noted that the two biggest packages include a Sharelink B612 router, while the rest of the deals are available as SIM-only contracts.